cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.RO

Reasoning: 
1. cs.AI - The paper introduces a deep reinforcement learning agent that learns to beat Atari games with the aid of natural language instructions, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence.
2. cs.CL - The paper involves the use of natural language instructions to guide the reinforcement learning agent, which falls under the category of computational linguistics.
3. cs.LG - The paper involves the use of deep learning techniques to train the reinforcement learning agent, which falls under the category of machine learning.
4. cs.CV - The paper involves the use of visual observations from the Atari games to train the reinforcement learning agent, which falls under the category of computer vision.
5. cs.RO - The paper involves the use of a reinforcement learning agent to control an agent in a physical environment, which falls under the category of robotics.
